[SPEAKER_00]: We'll take a vote.

76
00:06:37,184 --> 00:06:38,044
[SPEAKER_00]: Dr. Plattowitz?

77
00:06:38,504 --> 00:06:38,784
[SPEAKER_05]: Yes.

